raw_data.title: HEI Install
raw_data.description: Install all security systems related equipment as designed for the security systems functions. Requires: Associates degree in Electronics or Trade School or relevant technical related field, or equivalent experience and Manufacturer Certifications. Specific Vendor related certification for various systems and related integration functions. Minimum three years experience.
raw_data.education_and_experience_substitution: One year of relevant experience may be substituted for each year of educational experience; 2 years of exp is equivalent to an associate’s degree; 4 years of exp is equivalent to a bachelor’s degree. With regard to educational degrees, the following equivalencies apply: A Professional Engineer (PE) certification is equivalent to a BS. An industry recognized apprentice craft training program is equivalent to an AA for an electronics technician. A DOD-sponsored technical training school apprentice program is equivalent to an AA.Completion of a Military Class A and/or Class B school is equivalent to an AA.
raw_data.required_certifications_or_licenses: Security Manufacturer and or Vendor Certifications
